00:06:26.437 --> 00:06:28.447
turn out to be quite the bargain.

00:06:30.087 --> 00:06:37.387
In 2018 the acquisition was complete, and
Musical.ly merged with TikTok, becoming

00:06:37.387 --> 00:06:43.447
one joint app, with the copied app buying
