00:23:10.219 --> 00:23:14.417
Certainly, there is no doubt that
it has inspired a vast amount of

00:23:14.417 --> 00:23:18.797
creativity, and brought joy to
billions of people around the world.

00:23:19.887 --> 00:23:24.377
The question remains though,
about what unforeseen other things

00:23:24.667 --> 00:23:26.117
it might have brought with it.

